Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:14.02,HUD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mode/ {\c&H6860CA&}Combat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:14.02,HUD2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe \NRace: Half-Alv \NEnchanter, Level 90
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.46,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Electrical Fuzz!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming seven briar weasels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.43,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Careful! To your right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:33.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:36.72,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:42.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These things are tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to use a Shield Smash... What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:47.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,These controls suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two from the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:52.11,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They stink... Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:56.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to grasp a situation \Nwhen the field of vision is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.16,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:00:59.33,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Same here, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's all I can do to hold them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:03.73,HUD2,A,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki \NRace/ Human \NAssassin Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:04.49,HUD3,A,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu \NRace/ Human \NGuardian, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:04.35,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu! Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:04.49,HUD2,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe \NRace: Half-Alv \NEnchanter, Level 90
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:05.45,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:06.12,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:10.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like a game at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:12.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:14.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our new reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.35,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:21.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:21.97,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:23.79,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use a Nightmare Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:27.70,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,A triffid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Where did it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:30.06,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:30.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.99,HUD4,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Enchanter, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:21.04,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden, there I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:27.81,Title1,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1752,1)}The Apocalypse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.48,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.53,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of moisture in the air, \Nand the bright sunlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Silverleaf Tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.64,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.95,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Akihabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.00,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.30,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.63,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.98,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Get me the GM!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.99,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:14.44,Default,NPC,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.03,HUD1,NPC,0000,0000,0000,,Skills \N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NQuest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.03,SignB,NPC,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment \N\N\N\N\N\NItems
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a status screen, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.67,HUD Big,,0000,0000,0000,,Items
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:41.17,HUD2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dezanegg's Magic Bag
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can control it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:50.29,Green HUD,S,0000,0000,0000,,Log Out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No good... It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:51.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.52,Green HUD,S,0000,0000,0000,,Friend List
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.14,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,My friend list!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:58.48,Green HUD,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend List
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.82,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,If their names are lit up, \Ndoes that mean they're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.28,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Even Tohya and Minori are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.57,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.81,HUD Big,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}No Guild \NNaotsugu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.43,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,I know, voice chat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:12.14,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,If I can talk to him via telepathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro? Is that you, Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:22.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.94,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:33.47,HUD2,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu \NRace/ Human \NGuardian, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:38.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just, you look the way I pictured you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.88,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:44.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,An intelligent man, with glasses \Nand nasty, beady eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,My race is supposed to be Half-Alv...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.68,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So, I log in for the first time in two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:56.62,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me anything you know, nasty-glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:00.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears we're in the world of {\i1}Elder Tale{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't today the day they planned \Nto add the new expansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.97,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, The Novasphere Pioneers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Up until the second they executed the \Nupdate, I can remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And the next thing I knew, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:25.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.95,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it hundreds of times in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.26,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sky stretches so much further.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:38.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And it feels like I'm really touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.81,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this isn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.49,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're in the game, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.69,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that only happened in fantasy novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.60,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You think we can get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:02.20,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How did we get here, in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I know... We may not be \Nable to return quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:09.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We should be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We have to know more about this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:22.88,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you as calm \Nand analytical as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Calm isn't the word I'd choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I know this isn't what you expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,but welcome back to {\i1}Elder Tale{\i0}, Naotsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:39.89,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.53,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The buildings and roads \Nwere just as I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.28,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, just like the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.08,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I can use my items...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:59.08,Green HUD,S,0000,0000,0000,,Quest Items \NFood         Potions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.69,Default - margin,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As well as my magic and skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:02.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like we can't log out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I checked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Want to have a look at the outside zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:09.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.37,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.92,Default,Party,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure monsters are out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.38,Default,Party,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:19.39,Default,Party,0000,0000,0000,,You go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.65,Default,Party,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, no... You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.90,Default,Party,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.51,Default,Party,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:25.27,Default,Party,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Someone, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If you're back in the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,you work must have calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:32.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.81,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What really sucks is there \Naren't any cute girls at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:37.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.65,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.03,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a closet pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a closet anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.21,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,There are two types of men in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.93,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Open perverts who admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:51.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,and closet perverts who won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.76,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I am the former!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And I love panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.35,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You are the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.93,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And I know you love them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.65,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How tall are you, Naotsugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.24,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,183 cm,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.33,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,just like in {\i1}Elder Tale{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:18.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,My character is taller than I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:21.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So this body doesn't feel quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.50,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for showing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.62,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:30.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,To some degree, your game character \Nreflects your real self.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.01,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:35.57,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:37.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:42.35,HUD3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Akatsuki \NRace/ Human \NAssassin Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.35,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What? You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We were in a party together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:49.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not much of a talker, but a good assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So you're also here, Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:59.19,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Naotsugu, a guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.17,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you're an open \Npervert or not, let's get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:04.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You say that to someone you just met?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.04,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.16,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to sell me a potion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:15.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,An appearance-changing potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.19,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki, you're a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you never spoke much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.19,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Appearance-changing potions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Those are rare. \NThey only distributed them once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.15,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered Shiroe had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wouldn't use voice chat \Nbecause you were playing as an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:48.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.80,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,She's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:12.86,HUD2,{Sex,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki \NRace/ Human \NAssassin Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:12.86,SignC,{Sex,0000,0000,0000,,Female
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.02,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I retract my earlier statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:28.21,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be either an open pervert \Nor a closet one, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.04,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, is there something wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,There are many things wrong with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.09,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he's messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, Akatsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:47.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,did you adjust your character \Nto be closer to your real size?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:47.97,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.28,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You should have done that in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:55.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Games are fun because you can do things \Nyou couldn't in real life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But once I was stuck here, \Nit was very inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.57,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Inconvenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You mean like the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:09.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, is it all right if I knee \Nthis strange man in the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ask {\i1}before{\i0} you do it, shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.17,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me a shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how much do I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:24.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone saying \NI wouldn't repay a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:29.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,If it's that big a deal, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:36.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, is it all right if I knee \Nthis strange man in the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.96,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I said to ask {\i1}before{\i0} you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:41.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't even finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:43.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You were about to say something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I was, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.57,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, why don't you stay with us for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Strategist! Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:57.50,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's true... We can't leave her by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.90,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you refuse to join a guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:04.38,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Assassins are lone wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't in one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:12.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I think it's better to \Nstay in a group than go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right with that, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be happy to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:26.36,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as a ninja, I shall revere you as my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja? Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't she an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:35.16,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You have saved me from the dire fate \Nof being transformed into a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I must work to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.85,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That is what requiting a debt means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:45.44,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, as your ninja, I shall protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:50.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.30,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:05.62,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't more People of the \NLand around than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.15,Green HUD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an7}Albel/ People of the Land
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:10.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The NPCs that inhabit the world of{\i0} Elder Tale
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.27,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,call themselves People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:19.95,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,And we players are called adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.13,Default,NPC,0000,0000,0000,,Want to buy something, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we can eat these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No time to waste thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take rice dumplings and green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.42,Default,NPC,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.49,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.44,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They all taste the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:46.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like a soggy cracker, without salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:49.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And all the drinks taste like water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.74,Yellow Phone,S,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:53.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:55.82,Green HUD,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Marielle \NCrescent Moon Alliance \NWelcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:14:59.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,From Marielle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.38,SignD,S,0000,0000,0000,,Guild Building {\fs18}\NJapan Server \NAkihabara \NCity/ No Monsters \NNo PVP \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:03.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she leads the guild known \Nas the Crescent Moon Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:08.08,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird how the guild building \Nis nothing but doors, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:11.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Each Guild Hall is its own zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Only the really weird stuff is still like a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.76,SignD,N,0000,0000,0000,,Guild Hall 236 \N{\fs18}Guild Master: Marielle \NGuild Name: Crescent Moon Alliance\N\NEntry Restrictions: Yes\N\NID: Shiroe    No Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is the guild master's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:27.87,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:27.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? You must be hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:34.69,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Eat something... Not that it has any flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.25,SignD,S,0000,0000,0000,,Marielle \N{\fs20}Race/ Elf \NCleric \NGuild Master: \NCrescent Moon Alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:39.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.90,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a girlfriend now, Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.90,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.88,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.41,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Want a lollipop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:52.29,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro, where were you hiding this hot chick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been hiding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.22,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.93,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:04.41,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty buff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:06.00,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You play sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.65,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.67,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What is her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:12.97,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,She's scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:15.02,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.57,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hot girls everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:22.16,SignD,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Henrietta \N{\fs18}Race/ Human \NBard \NCrescent Moon Alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:21.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.63,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:25.79,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for summoning you here, Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:30.11,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Given what's happening, I'd like \Nto exchange information...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.59,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.99,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,There they go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.94,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to share information?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the Crescent \NMoon Alliance members?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:55.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Including myself, nineteen are online.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.53,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen are in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen of nineteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:07.21,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that, along with Akihabara, the other \Nfour major cities on the Japanese server,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.63,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Shibuya, Minami, Susukino, and Nakasu \Nare all in the same shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:15.63,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,And the inter-city transport gates are offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:20.14,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, teleporting elsewhere is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:27.34,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The Akihabara adventurers are all meeting \Nwith their guilds, just like we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:32.53,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Some guilds are also looking to recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:38.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this, the more people \Non your side, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:41.06,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But even if this isn't our world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,we're all very familiar with {\i1}Elder Tale{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the new expansion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Novasphere Pioneers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:53.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,If they've added that new expansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then monsters, items, and quests \Nmay all be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:06.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This world may not be the {\i1}Elder Tale{\i0} we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.36,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Shiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:21.28,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I know you aren't a big fan of guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.52,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to join ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.67,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.05,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Debauchery Tea Party is gone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:39.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.57,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great guild master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:51.05,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's all she can do to stay under control, \Nbut she's still acting so friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:58.09,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Debauchery Tea Party a \Nlegendary guild that disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:59.36,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The Tea Party wasn't a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:05.25,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It was a small group that \Nnever formed a guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:09.90,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,but managed to complete several \Nlarge-scale battles called raids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:13.96,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,And Shiroe was their strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we going to be stuck here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.97,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,How long will they just sit around there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Die and you can escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In stories like this, that's pretty common.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes, if you die in \Nthe game, you die in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:32.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,When it was just a game, \Nyou'd revive at the Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.19,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't very well experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:40.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you do revive, \Nwhat about your penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.88,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Archive Tower Forests?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We're level 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:56.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's the level cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, low-level monsters \Nwould just ignore us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But in this area, the monsters will aggro on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,So it's the perfect place to try it, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:11.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You can't use your \Nmini-map in the outside zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:13.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Briar Weasels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Level 28...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.69,Monsters,S,0000,0000,0000,,Briar Weasel \NRank/ Normal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.77,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.70,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to enter commands while \Nmonsters are running at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.64,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's a difference between \N"using" and "mastering"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Get into formation, as discussed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.58,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt as much as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.75,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,But unlike when you play the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.71,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,trying to fight monsters in front,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:44.74,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,while keeping an eye on your \Nparty and overall situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.72,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.47,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,To survive in this world, we must
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:56.77,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,hurry and learn its rules and how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.28,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,But what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:07.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My body just moved on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use your commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to use your body to feel the motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.80,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:25.80,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it, but fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:28.18,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.02,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:42.12,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,An MMORPG with over twenty \Nmillion worldwide players.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:48.49,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Without warning, an estimated thirty \Nthousand Japanese alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:51.72,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,And several hundred thousand worldwide...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.99,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Were trapped in a world just like the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:58.04,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nightmare Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:03.92,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Cross Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:06.43,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Assassinate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:10.57,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Later, they would come to call this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:12.81,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:19.36,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Serara, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.98,SignD,M,0000,0000,0000,,Serara \N{\fs18}Crescent Moon Alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.98,SignD,M,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Susukino\N{\fs18}Japan Server\NEdge Zone/ Susukino \NCity/ No Monsters \NNo PVP \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:20.90,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Serara...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:21.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Marielle, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:26.99,Default,Thug,0000,0000,0000,,We found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.12,Default,Thug,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:34.71,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Serara!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:09.00,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,One day, we found ourselves \Ntrapped in another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.57,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,There, we fought and hurt one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:14.51,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,But it was only a game, \Nto keep our minds off the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:17.05,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,that we weren't even allowed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:20.02,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,When a young girl in the \NCrescent Moon Alliance, Serara,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:23.73,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,runs into danger in a distant northern \Nland, Shiroe sets out on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.73,0:24:26.09,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Battle Of Loka.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:31.01,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle of Loka
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.09,0:24:28.32,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,This is our reality.
